{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake, ament-cmake-gtest, ament-lint-auto, ament-lint-common, builtin-interfaces, geometry-msgs, rosidl-cmake, rosidl-default-generators, rosidl-default-runtime, std-msgs }:
